Publisher Description

Kissflow Digital Workplace is the one tool to manage any type of work that comes your way.

Use Kissflow in four main ways:

* Process management to bring easy automation into all of your predictable work

* Project management to organize teams and coordinate work with value stream mapping

* Case management to solve bug tracking, ticketing, and processes that require multiple resolutions

* Collaboration to discuss and share with specific work groups

The mobile app gives you access to initiate, track, and approve process items and keep conversations moving even while you are on the go.

Organizations around the world use Kissflow to move their teams away from spreadsheets and email and onto a platform that reduces chaos and keeps the focus on getting work done.

About Kissflow Digital Workplace

Kissflow Digital Workplace is a free app for iOS published in the Office Suites & Tools list of apps, part of Business.

The company that develops Kissflow Digital Workplace is OrangeScape. The latest version released by its developer is 1.0.27.

To install Kissflow Digital Workplace on your iOS device, just click the green Continue To App button above to start the installation process. The app is listed on our website since 2024-07-25 and was downloaded 1 times. We have already checked if the download link is safe, however for your own protection we recommend that you scan the downloaded app with your antivirus. Your antivirus may detect the Kissflow Digital Workplace as malware if the download link is broken.

How to install Kissflow Digital Workplace on your iOS device:

Click on the Continue To App button on our website. This will redirect you to the App Store.

Once the Kissflow Digital Workplace is shown in the iTunes listing of your iOS device, you can start its download and installation. Tap on the GET button to the right of the app to start downloading it.

If you are not logged-in the iOS appstore app, you'll be prompted for your your Apple ID and/or password.

After Kissflow Digital Workplace is downloaded, you'll see an INSTALL button to the right. Tap on it to start the actual installation of the iOS app.

Once installation is finished you can tap on the OPEN button to start it. Its icon will also be added to your device home screen.
